Package: qfwr
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Tutorials for "Quantitative Finance with R"
Version: 0.1.01
Author: Yongyi Zeng
Maintainer: Yongyi Zeng <zzyy@xmu.edu.cn>
Description: Interactive tutorials for my course "Quantitative Finance 
    with R" (QFwR) to facilitate teaching and learning. The interactive 
    exercises are mainly powered by RStudio's `learnr`, Datacamp's 
    `testwhat` package and some ideas / codes stolen with pride from 
    Prof. Rundel's `learnrhash`.
URL: https://github.com/qfwr2022/qfwr
BugReports: https://github.com/qfwr2022/qfwr/issues
